technologies.name: Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Data
technologies.evidence: The Autoscriber App takes structured clinical notes for you in real-time during conversations with patients. Autoscriber Ambient Listening Solutions streamline clinical documentation by using AI to capture, transcribe, and organise conversations in real time.

technologies.name: Cybersecurity
technologies.evidence: ISO certified, GDPR and EU AI Act compliant. Autoscriber protects patient data and assures healthcare providers of a secure, responsible AI tool in their practice.
